{
  "stem": "10162.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 89.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did the whole thing from, from, from A to Z, you know, filling with this poisonous-- he would call it tri-- tri something, I forget-- the grenades.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- I did work for a short time at the filling station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then soon after that, they put me at the very end of the mass production, you know, when the things just come rolling down, where my job was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was-- I think I was probably the tallest there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, I, I had broad shoulders and round face, something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They thought I was just strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to pick these grenades, the way they rolled up, and flip it-- put it over into a, a little trolley kind of thing that had grates.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And probably 16 would go into one of these things and that rolled right out of the building and where, on the other side, were the Russian prisoners of war who would-- who would put it in trains.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked there until April '45, until April 6 or something like that, '45.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't know, nine months, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was better conditions in the-- definitely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we especially appreciated the better conditions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, of course, it got-- you know, it got very difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we had to-- these grenades I had to carry were, were-- weighed almost as much as I did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very hard for me to pick up even one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the first few days when we went back-- these were all night shifts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to run back after 12 hours and there we were given the dinner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And with the spoon, I couldn't hold the spoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My hands were just-- I just couldn't hold it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My fingers were swollen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I complained, oh, it's so heavy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said, you better do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because next week, you have to do 36 and the week after that, I don't know, 50 and you have to do up to, I don't know, 120 a night.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it just sounded like it's an impossibility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I must say I did it even with ease at-- you know, I just-- it somehow-- in the first time in my life, I-- I realized that-- how, how with, with, with smarts, you can figure out how to do things.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, I flipped it this way and I flipped it that way and I just got it in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I almost liked it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just-- I felt like I was doing something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was proud of myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they picked-- at that time, they picked 1,000 young Hungarian women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were there toward the end, was almost-- there, there were-- was no more raids even, because they were-- the American planes were constantly overhead.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, they would come down so low that we could see the pilot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, we always had this unshakable faith that they know who we are and that we were happy when we saw the bombs falling next to us anywhere because they knew that they know who we are and they're not going to, to, to drop anything on us.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were running right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were just saying good, good, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so one day, they just evacuated the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started this march toward the center of Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were mostly marching in the dark at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
